{
  "texts": [
    "This type of interaction assists both parties in achieving common goals [71].",
    "However, feature-based explanation methods do not correspond to human cognition and are difficult to communicate with domain experts.",
    "Concept-supported interpretations, on the other hand, facilitate efficient communication between human experts and complex models.",
    "These effective human-AI collaborations enable human intervention to provide appropriate and straightforward feedback to aid system enhancement at a higher level.",
    "As a result of concept-supported methods, we can achieve Active Learning [210], in which domain experts are actively involved in the learning process."
  ]
}